swagger/to-html.html.body: Swagger to HTML Download Schema Swagger store Version: 1.0.0 This is a sample server Petstore server. You can find out more about Swagger at [http://swagger.io](http://swagger.io) or on [irc.freenode.net, #swagger](http://swagger.io/irc/). For this sample, you can use the api key `special-key` to test the authorization filters. Security Definitions petstore_auth The type of security scheme is oauth2 . The flow used by the OAuth2 security scheme is implicit . The authorization URL to be used for this flow is http://petstore.swagger.io/oauth/dialog . The available scopes for the OAuth2 security scheme are as follows. write:pets : modify pets in your account read:pets : read your pets api_key The type of security scheme is apiKey . The name of the header to be used is api_key . Add a new pet to the store POST /pet Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Request Body id integer (int64) category object category.id integer (int64) category.name string name string required Eg. doggie photoUrls array required photoUrls[] string tags array tags[] object tags[].id integer (int64) tags[].name string status enum pet status in the store Allowed values: available , pending , sold . curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 405 Invalid input Reference Update an existing pet PUT /pet Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Request Body id integer (int64) category object category.id integer (int64) category.name string name string required Eg. doggie photoUrls array required photoUrls[] string tags array tags[] object tags[].id integer (int64) tags[].name string status enum pet status in the store Allowed values: available , pending , sold . curl -v -X PUT https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 400 Invalid ID supplied Reference Status Code: 404 Pet not found Reference Status Code: 405 Validation exception Reference Finds Pets by status Multiple status values can be provided with comma separated strings GET /pet/findByStatus Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Path status array required Used in query Status values that need to be considered for filter curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/findByStatus Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference [] object [].id integer (int64) [].category object [].category.id integer (int64) [].category.name string [].name string required Eg. doggie [].photoUrls array required [].photoUrls[] string [].tags array [].tags[] object [].tags[].id integer (int64) [].tags[].name string [].status enum pet status in the store Allowed values: available , pending , sold . Status Code: 400 Invalid status value Reference Finds Pets by tags Muliple tags can be provided with comma separated strings. Use tag1, tag2, tag3 for testing. GET /pet/findByTags Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Path tags array required Used in query Tags to filter by curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/findByTags Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference [] object [].id integer (int64) [].category object [].category.id integer (int64) [].category.name string [].name string required Eg. doggie [].photoUrls array required [].photoUrls[] string [].tags array [].tags[] object [].tags[].id integer (int64) [].tags[].name string [].status enum pet status in the store Allowed values: available , pending , sold . Status Code: 400 Invalid tag value Reference Find pet by ID Returns a single pet GET /pet/{petId} Security Requirement Request Sample Request Path petId integer (int64) required Used in path ID of pet to return curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/{petId} Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference id integer (int64) category object category.id integer (int64) category.name string name string required Eg. doggie photoUrls array required photoUrls[] string tags array tags[] object tags[].id integer (int64) tags[].name string status enum pet status in the store Allowed values: available , pending , sold . Status Code: 400 Invalid ID supplied Reference Status Code: 404 Pet not found Reference Updates a pet in the store with form data POST /pet/{petId} Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Path petId integer (int64) required Used in path ID of pet that needs to be updated Request Body name string Used in formData Updated name of the pet status string Used in formData Updated status of the pet curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/{petId} \ -F "name: undefined" \ -F "status: undefined" Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 405 Invalid input Reference Deletes a pet DELETE /pet/{petId} Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Header api_key string Path petId integer (int64) required Used in path Pet id to delete curl -v -X DELETE https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/{petId} \ -H "api_key: undefined" Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 400 Invalid ID supplied Reference Status Code: 404 Pet not found Reference uploads an image POST /pet/{petId}/uploadImage Security Requirement write:pets and read:pets scopes are required for petstore_auth . Request Sample Request Path petId integer (int64) required Used in path ID of pet to update Request Body additionalMetadata string Used in formData Additional data to pass to server file file Used in formData file to upload curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/pet/{petId}/uploadImage \ -F "additionalMetadata: undefined" \ -F "file: undefined" Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference code integer (int32) type string message string Returns pet inventories by status Returns a map of status codes to quantities GET /store/inventory Security Requirement Request Sample Request curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/store/inventory Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference Place an order for a pet POST /store/order Request Sample Request Request Body id integer (int64) petId integer (int64) quantity integer (int32) shipDate string (date-time) status enum Order Status Allowed values: placed , approved , delivered . complete boolean curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/store/order Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference id integer (int64) petId integer (int64) quantity integer (int32) shipDate string (date-time) status enum Order Status Allowed values: placed , approved , delivered . complete boolean Status Code: 400 Invalid Order Reference Find purchase order by ID For valid response try integer IDs with value = 1 and = 10. Other values will generated exceptions GET /store/order/{orderId} Request Sample Request Path orderId integer (int64) required Used in path ID of pet that needs to be fetched curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/store/order/{orderId} Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference id integer (int64) petId integer (int64) quantity integer (int32) shipDate string (date-time) status enum Order Status Allowed values: placed , approved , delivered . complete boolean Status Code: 400 Invalid ID supplied Reference Status Code: 404 Order not found Reference Delete purchase order by ID For valid response try integer IDs with positive integer value. Negative or non-integer values will generate API errors DELETE /store/order/{orderId} Request Sample Request Path orderId integer (int64) required Used in path ID of the order that needs to be deleted curl -v -X DELETE https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/store/order/{orderId} Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 400 Invalid ID supplied Reference Status Code: 404 Order not found Reference Create user This can only be done by the logged in user. POST /user Request Sample Request Request Body id integer (int64) username string firstName string lastName string email string password string phone string userStatus integer (int32) User Status curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user Copy Request Response Sample Response This is a default response for the request. successful operation Reference Creates list of users with given input array POST /user/createWithArray Request Sample Request Request Body [] object [].id integer (int64) [].username string [].firstName string [].lastName string [].email string [].password string [].phone string [].userStatus integer (int32) User Status curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user/createWithArray Copy Request Response Sample Response This is a default response for the request. successful operation Reference Creates list of users with given input array POST /user/createWithList Request Sample Request Request Body [] object [].id integer (int64) [].username string [].firstName string [].lastName string [].email string [].password string [].phone string [].userStatus integer (int32) User Status curl -v -X POST https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user/createWithList Copy Request Response Sample Response This is a default response for the request. successful operation Reference Logs user into the system GET /user/login Request Sample Request Path username string required Used in query The user name for login password string required Used in query The password for login in clear text curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user/login Copy Request Use user1 for testing. curl -v -X GET https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user/{username} Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 200 successful operation Reference id integer (int64) username string firstName string lastName string email string password string phone string userStatus integer (int32) User Status Status Code: 400 Invalid username supplied Reference Status Code: 404 User not found Reference Updated user This can only be done by the logged in user. PUT /user/{username} Request Sample Request Path username string required Used in path name that need to be updated Request Body id integer (int64) username string firstName string lastName string email string password string phone string userStatus integer (int32) User Status curl -v -X PUT https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user/{username} Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 400 Invalid user supplied Reference Status Code: 404 User not found Reference Delete user This can only be done by the logged in user. DELETE /user/{username} Request Sample Request Path username string required Used in path The name that needs to be deleted curl -v -X DELETE https://petstore.swagger.io/v2/user/{username} Copy Request Response Sample Response Status Code: 400 Invalid username supplied Reference Status Code: 404 User not found Reference
